  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Starting <strong>1st April 2026</strong>, Back Market will apply a single blended payment fee of <strong>1%</strong> to all orders, no matter how your customer pays. This replaces variable fees by payment method and makes your costs more predictable. This change is included in the updated General Terms and Conditions that took effect on March 30, 2026.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Back Market provides secure payment services through payment partners that operate under their own terms and conditions.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong></strong></span></h3>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Available payment methods</strong></span></h2>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;width: 94.851%;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 47.627%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 52.3406%;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Payment method</strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Countries</strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 39.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Card</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">SE, FR, BE, DE, AT, ES, IT, UK, FI, PT, IE, GR, SK, NL</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 39.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">PayPal</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">UK, SE, FR, BE, DE, AT, ES, IT, SK, FI, PT, IE, GR, NL</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 39.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Apple Pay</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">UK, DE, FR, ES, NL, BE, IT, AT, FI, GR, IE, PT, SE, SK</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 39.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Google Pay</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">UK, DE, FR, ES, NL, BE, IT, AT, FI, GR, IE, PT, SE, SK</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 39.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Klarna Pay Now</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">SE, DE, NL, AT, UK</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 39.25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Klarna Pay Later (30 days)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">DE, AT, NL, FI, SE, UK</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Klarna Pay in 3</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">DE, UK, FR, ES, IT, PT, NL</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Oney 3x</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">FR, ES</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Oney 4x</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">FR, ES</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Oney 6x</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">ES</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Oney 10x</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">FR</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Oney 12x</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">FR</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">EPS (bank transfer)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">AT</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 25pt;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">iDeal (bank transfer)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">NL</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong></strong></span></h3>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>What&#39;s changing</strong></span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Before</strong></span></h3>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Payment fees vary by payment method, which makes your monthly costs harder to predict.</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Your invoices can show multiple payment-fee lines based on your customer&#39;s payment mix.</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>After (from 1st April 2026)</strong></span></h3>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A single <strong>1%</strong> payment fee applies to all orders, including PayPal and installment/buy now, pay later options.</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Your Back Market invoice will show <strong>one</strong> consolidated payment-fee line item.</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>How the 1% fee is calculated</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">The 1% blended payment fee is calculated on the listing price for each sale.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Example:</strong> If your listing price is <strong>$200</strong>, the payment fee will be <strong>$2</strong> (1% of $200).</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong></strong></span></h3>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>What you need to do</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">You don&#39;t need to change anything. The updated General Terms and Conditions took effect on <strong>March 30, 2026</strong>. By continuing to use Back Market after that date, you agreed to these updates (including the new payment fee structure).</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>What you&#39;ll see on your invoices (from 15 April 2026)</strong></span></h2>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">One payment-fee line item</span></p>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A <strong>1%</strong> fee rate for all orders</span></p>\n</li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong></strong></span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>FAQ</strong></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Where is this change documented?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">It’s included in the updated General Terms and Conditions, effective March 30, 2026.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Why is Back Market making this change?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">To make payment costs clearer and more predictable. Today, fees vary by payment method.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Does this apply to PayPal and installment/buy now, pay later payments?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Yes. The same <strong>1%</strong> blended fee applies to all payment methods.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>When does it start?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">April 1st, 2026.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Do I need to take any action?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">No. Only contact us if you want to refuse the updated Terms and Conditions.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>Are payment services still provided through payment partners?</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Yes. Back Market provides secure payment services through payment partners that operate under their own terms and conditions</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"></span></p>"
